WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
Your Linux dashboard. A native, touch-first home for the information you want at a glance.

00:05.000 --> 00:11.000
Live system widgets for CPU, GPU, memory, focus, media, time and everyday information.

00:11.000 --> 00:15.000
Portrait ready. Every widget reflows for the tall canvas.

00:15.000 --> 00:19.000
Turn the display. KScreen rotates the real panel and EdgeHub follows with a landscape layout.

00:19.000 --> 00:25.000
Edit from your desktop. EdgeHub Manager mirrors the running Hub over a private local socket.

00:25.000 --> 00:31.000
Add screens live. A fifth screen arrives, and the Hub follows the selected screen.

00:31.000 --> 00:39.000
Preview portrait and landscape while arranging widgets, backgrounds and capacity.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.000
Switch themes, accents, backgrounds and wallpapers while the Hub is running.

00:45.000 --> 00:52.000
Thirty widgets. Nineteen preset screens. One live Manager.
